24e99069-88c5-43bf-92c5-0895f0bb6d1a.name: The architecture of Babylon is mudbrick, fired brick and bitumen, with many of its buildings designed to protect from heat and sun.

93bbc4ee-1811-4509-9621-82b144bc5557.name: Babylon is a Mesopotamian city located near the Euphrates river, with a climate of very hot and dry summers and short winters.

55161c44-8145-4917-b9bd-f372679ae739.name: The year is 500 BC and it is the reign of Nebuchadnezzar II
